2.10	The_Bravados	The Bravados	The Bravados is a 1958 western film (color by DeLuxe), directed by Henry King starring Gregory Peck and Joan Collins. The CinemaScope film was based on a novel of the same name written by Frank O'Rourke.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/28/The_Bravados_-_US_film_poster.jpg/220px-The_Bravados_-_US_film_poster.jpg
